Static Scoping [静态作用域]
• Scopes formed by where definitions are in program text[声明起作用
的那段区域] 
Also known as lexical scoping since related to program text C/C++, Java, 
Python, JavaScript[也叫词法作用域] 
• Rule: bind to the closest enclosing definition 
88
void foo() 
{ 
char x;
...
{ 
int x;
… 
} 
x = x + 1;
}

Dynamic Scoping[动态作用域]
• Scopes formed by when definitions happen during runtime[运行时
决定] 
Perl, Bash, LISP, Scheme 
• Rule: bind to most recent definition in current execution 
• Which x’s definition is the most recent? 
Execution (a): ...(1)...(2)...(5) 
Execution (b): ...(1)...(2)...(3)...(4)...(5)
